Package: vlightr
Type: Package
Title: Persistent Conditional Formatting for Vectors
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: utils::person(
  "Ethan", "Sansom", 
  email = "ethan.sansom29@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre")
  )
Description: Provides a generic vector class with persistant conditional formatting. 
    `highlight` an arbitrary vector to color, emphasize, or otherwise reformat 
    elements of interest when printed as a vector or tibble column. Make
    exploratory data analysis and interactive data validation easier on the eyes.
